---> PASSIVE VOICE (Edilgen Çatı)                                                     prepared by Uğur ARSLAN, @arslanuguur 

** Subject ve Object yerini değiştiriyor

Active Voice
                          S     V       O
	                        Onlar kalemi kırdı
	                        They broke the pen
	                        S	   V	   O

Passive Voice
                          S      O     p          V
                        	Kalem, onlar tarafından kırıldı
	                        The pen is broken by them
                          S	      V		      p  O


                                                                          V3
Tense                       Active                                        Passive                                                                           
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Present Simple              He solves the problem                         The problem is solved by him
Present Continuous          She is making a cake                          A cake is being made by her
Present Perfect             They have already discussed the book          The book has already been discussed.
Present Perfect Cont.       *	  
Past Simple                 Mercedes made this car                        This car was made by Mercedes
Past Continuous	            The salesman was helping the customer         The customer was being helped
Past Perfect                I had made a cake                             A cake had been made by me
Past Perfect Cont.          *  
Future Simple/Going to      The company will hire new workers             New workers will be hired by the company
                            They are going to televise the match          The match is going to be televised by them
Future Continuous           *	      
Future Perfect              They will have finished the work              The work will have been finished by them
Future Perfect Cont.        *


Modal	                    
                            He has to solve the problem                   The problem has to be solved by me
                            She must deliver the letters                  The letters must be delivered
                            The manager should interview me               I should have been intervied by the manager
Modal Perfect
                            We should have shipped the goods              The goods should have been shipped by us
                            He might have served dinner                   Dinner might have been served




EXAMPLES:
she wasn't told                                                                         ona söylenmedi
I was told to stay at home                                                              evde kalmam söylendi
we were told not to leave the class                                                     bize sınıftan dışarı çıkılmamamız söylendi
the child that was not embraced by the village, will burn it down to feel its warmth    köy tarafından kucaklanmayan çocuk, sıcaklığını hissetmek için köyü yakar
bullets only do their jobs after they are fired                                         kurşunlar sadece ateşlendikten sonra işlerini yapar 
interest rates will probably be increased next year                                     faiz oranları muhtemelen gelecek yıl artırılacaktır
who were you introduced to at the meeting? anyone interesting?                          toplantıda kimlerle tanıştırıldın, ilginç herhangi biri? 
the Christmas cakes are already being distributed                                       Noel pastaları şimdiden dağıtılıyor
my grandmother was born in 1913                                                         babaannem 1913'de doğdu
the grapes are picked in September. Then they are packaged and sent to shops            üzümler eylül ayında toplanır. daha sonra paketlenir ve dükkanlara gönderilir
we haven’t been informed about the new price list yet                                   yeni fiyat listesi hakkında henüz bilgilendirilmedik
this book was written by Aldous Huxley. Have you read it?                               Bu kitap Aldous Huxley tarafından yazılmıştır. Onu okudun mu? 
when we arrived, our bags had already been taken to our room                            vardığımızda çantalarımız çoktan odamıza alınmıştı 
your shirts will have been washed and ironed by 6 pm                                    gömlekleriniz akşam 6'ya kadar yıkanmış ve ütülenmiş olacak
my car was being cleaned when it started to rain                                        arabam yağmur yağmaya başladığında temizleniyordu
the ambulance drivers are helped by volunteers                                          Ambulans şoförlerine gönüllüler yardım ediyor 
the Cathedral was built in the 14th Century                                             bu katedral 14üncü yüzyılda inşa edilmiş
the roads are cleaned once a week                                                       yollar haftada bir kez temizlenir
the Gioconda was painted by Leonardo da Vinci                                           Gioconda, Leonardo da Vinci tarafından boyandı 
"Catch Me If You Can" was directed by Steven Spielberg                                  "sıkıysa yakala" filmi Steven Spielberg tarafından yönetildi
six people have been arrested in a raid (six arrested in raid)                          operasyonda altı kişi tutuklandı 
the criminal was arrested as he came out of the bank                                    suçlu bankadan çıkarken tutuklandı
I want to live the life is chosen by myself, not what is offered to me                  ben bana sunulan değil, kendi seçtiğim hayatı yaşamak istiyorum
the blunders are all there on the board, waiting to be made                             tahtada yapılmayı bekleyen tüm hatalar / gaflar / falsolar vardır


